WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.520
They applauded the demo, felt good.

00:05.520 --> 00:10.960
I usually say I draw the architecture because it's what people expect.

00:10.960 --> 00:20.880
But behind the applause, I mostly copied patterns, reused scripts, and assembled other people's

00:20.880 --> 00:24.280
modules.

00:24.280 --> 00:29.480
Once in a while, I told myself that stitching counts as designing.

00:29.480 --> 00:32.240
It's not a lie, so much as a convenience.

